Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:10.99,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:36.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto of the Third Eye, a part \Nof the organization known as
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:39.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Eye of the Midnight Sun that \Nseeks to destroy the Clover Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:41.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,infiltrated the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:45.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His power was so great that Asta and the \Nothers fell to him, one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But Noelle diligently faced off with Vetto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.83,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,in order to protect her friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:07.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Noelle Silva of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:10.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt my friends and comrades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:14.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:43.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as though Noelle's attack \Nhad finally defeated Vetto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:46.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but the battle wasn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:53.13,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive... You managed \Nto draw me out, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.97,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.94,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:14.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.32,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! I'm going to go get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.89,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You two tend to as many people as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:22.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:29.69,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,What's this horrifying mana I'm sensing \Nfrom the bottom of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.25,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the beast from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.29,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is even worse. It's no beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.26,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's a monster that's way \Nmore powerful than a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:46.77,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What is this ominous mana? \NI've never felt anything like it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:53.06,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Does Lord Vetto's power concern you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:56.32,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,You must be buzzing with confidence, \Nto look away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:57.86,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.74,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the people \Nthe captain mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.97,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Third Eye, the strongest group \Nin the Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.75,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who infiltrated the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.46,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Sucks for you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:14.34,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be exterminated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:18.57,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to suck all the magic out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.51,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:25.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you and find my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.09,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The way he looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:39.44,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like one of the fairy tales \NGranny used to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:45.69,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, there were evil fiends \Nthat lived in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:52.13,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted to make this world \Nand all of its magic their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:56.47,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest among them used forbidden magic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:59.46,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,to turn himself into a \Ndemon of incredible power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.34,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to exterminate humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:08.42,flashback,Granny,0000,0000,0000,,The one who stood against him\Nlater became the first Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:14.23,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This man is just like one of \Nthe fiends from that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.54,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.34,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.53,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That last spell drained all my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:19.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:24.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:28.09,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet? Yes, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:33.77,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now is when I show you true despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.64,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}The Only Weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:21.05,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you planning to do? \NYou can't leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave them alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:31.32,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,Useless, useless, it's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:32.93,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:39.32,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever escaped my Spatial Magic:\N Different Dimension Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:45.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Hurry up and let me \Nout of here, or you'll be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.53,main,Abari,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, well, aren't you scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.27,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat the shit out of you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! It's too late to apologize now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.03,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.75,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this guy is violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.37,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito Magic: Mosquito Hum!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:38.04,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell? You're trying\Nto suck blood from a stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.59,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This sound's going to make me go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:54.81,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? It's like\Nyou've suffered a painful bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:09:00.60,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito Magic: Mana-Sucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.67,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how long you \Ncan keep buzzing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.45,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to destroy you Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:20.87,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,so that we, the Eye of the Midnight \NSun, can fulfill our great desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.83,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Not able to run anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.51,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,M-My arm won't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.22,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just your arm that won't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.40,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.86,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for moving closer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If you were too far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:54.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,my threads would've been \Nblown away by the sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:10:00.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I? That I was going to \Ndefeat you and go to my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.29,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thread Magic: Dancing Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.20,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body's bugging out on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.42,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:17.92,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Suck up as much magic as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:21.22,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll have to settle for your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:30.19,main,Teuke,0000,0000,0000,,M-My magic's... being sucked away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:41.95,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness. I'm going to replenish \Nall the mana that was wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.21,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.75,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:02.71,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can still stand,\Nanti-magic brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:05.06,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,But it's futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.97,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do when you're so beat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.63,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing mana
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:16.98,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,whispers to me that I should show you \Nvermin what true despair looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... You're badly hurt. How did you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:27.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono... used the last of \Nher strength to heal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,With a faint song...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:39.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.61,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:12:01.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pulverize this guy and heal \Nboth Kahono's throat and Kiato's leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:06.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even he managed to regrow an arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:10.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's someone out there \Nwho can use magic to heal them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:12.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That insane spell you did earlier... \NIt helped me get back onto my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:24.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as awesome as I thought you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.33,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, nope, nope, \Nnope, nope, nope, nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.80,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.35,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, nope, nope, \Nnope, nope, nope, nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.91,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:53.73,italics,Final,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to you? \NLook how beat up you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.19,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.37,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Especially against a monster like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:12:59.21,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.13,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:05.26,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,They are the strongest three \Nin the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.59,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:12.39,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... In combat, they surpass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.77,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.48,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,They're more powerful than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.11,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Third Eye, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:22.94,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He has to be bluffing when he says \Nthey're stronger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.24,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.35,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He does have much stronger magic than Licht,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.14,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,the leader of the Eye of the Midnight Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.45,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we could beat this guy,\Neven if we ganged up on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.87,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is already down for the count...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.21,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And he made this giant \Nhole with no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.87,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I'm going to escape through that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:54.47,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! There's no way I can save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.72,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I need to at least escape,\Nor we'll all be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.32,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, how pathetic you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:04.07,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do in that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:08.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't get cocky just \Nbecause you got another eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.58,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, nope, nope, nope, nope, \Nnope, nope! That guy's totally right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:16.28,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, this is impossible! \NThat guy's magic is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.96,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:21.04,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry up and run! \NNo, seriously, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:26.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned earlier that one of my \Nweak points is that I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:34.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my only weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:39.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm never going to give \Nup until I fulfill my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.77,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:57.58,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you just how \Nuseless that weapon is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:03.04,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you exactly what despair means!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:09.77,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Before I defeat you lot, I should \Nprobably take out the trash first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:13.14,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:43.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear... Big and hairy over there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:47.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,must be the insane guy named Vetto \Nthe captain was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:51.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're way more ugly than I thought you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.84,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:01.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should've just passed out drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:06.44,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But you really are insane, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:07.76,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.88,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't give up, and that's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:15.45,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and pull me along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:21.11,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why the other \NBlack Bulls liked you so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,and I think I finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:25.96,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:30.46,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, kid.\NJust like what Vanessa said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:34.97,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Because you didn't give up, Noelle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.55,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.72,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Magna, and Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:43.23,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,were all able to go beyond their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.60,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And... me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:54.20,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,A heart that refuses to \Ngive up is your only weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.23,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.74,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think that these cobwebs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.04,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,could keep a beast like me tied down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What fun would it be if you \Nactually stayed tied down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.67,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:14.79,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly think you can defeat me just \Nbecause another insect joined your cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.26,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:21.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.98,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,So there was still another mouse hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.55,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.91,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My juniors are working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.70,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That means I have to\Nact like a proper senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:50.04,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! What the heck am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:50.96,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:56.47,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you actually showed up.\NGood job, Finral the wuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:18:01.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I showed up! \NI'm no wuss, Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.14,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up! Don't give up! \NDon't give up! Don't give up! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.98,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You vermin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:14.15,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're ants. Less than vermin. \NNo matter how many of you gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.78,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,you won't even be able to scratch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:20.63,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, you have enough magic \Nto protect everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.79,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:30.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Still... his magic is unbelievable. Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:32.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.61,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I can't see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:39.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I definitely feel his ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:43.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If he manages to hit us head-on with any \Nof his attacks, it'll instantly be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:47.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's life or death right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:50.72,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts, damn it! I want to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If we get out of this alive, \NI'll give you a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A hug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:58.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You can cry all you want right into my bosom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:04.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral's ki just blew the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:08.49,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling guys is child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:13.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And for you, ordinary magic attacks \Nwon't work on him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.96,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You and your anti-magic will \Njust have to take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't let go of \Nthat sword, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:23.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Go give it all you've got. \NPut your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:25.31,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:29.56,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that we won't let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.19,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.70,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.08,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:09.33,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,My long-range attacks never \Neven touch the anti-magic sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:11.81,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The spatial magic user just \Nsends them right back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:17.07,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,For a mere human,\Nhe's quite fast and accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:20.18,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:22.07,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But I've gotta do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.07,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.82,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to pick \Nthem off at close range!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.54,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:44.59,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the spatial magic and\Nyour aura are gushing all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:49.72,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.64,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The thread changed his trajectory...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:58.25,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You scuttling little insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,with this weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:59.27,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:58.45,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:02.77,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Service Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:02.18,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Service Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:05.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's service magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:08.40,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Just like it sounds, it's magic \Nthat's a service to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:10.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:11.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:14.24,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All we've had lately is smelly \Nand hairy guys like Vetto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:16.79,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,hogging up all the screen time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:18.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:25.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So this is service magic!\NI wonder how Mimosa's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:28.42,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! That was a total success!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:30.79,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those perfect bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:33.05,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... The Black Bullsâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:36.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?! Stupidsta, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:37.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:42.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to work \Ntogether and defeat Vetto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.09,0:23:44.29,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Finral and I will assist you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.29,0:23:47.22,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able... no, \NI know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:51.17,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 48: "Despair vs. Hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 48\N\N{\fs18}Despair vs. Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:53.70,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is our magic!
